3e\u003cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e899834796943cd7184a457ea0c41579_1440w.jpg\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2558\" data-rawheight=\"1378\" data-original-token=\"v2-e899834796943cd7184a457ea0c41579\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2b9f05d0554e1007acc95f46de2dbbba_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2558\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e899834796943cd7184a457ea0c41579_r.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003espark主界面\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-081286f63ae55cb53353676beea9bd15_1440w.jpg\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2558\" data-rawheight=\"1378\" data-original-token=\"v2-081286f63ae55cb53353676beea9bd15\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-315080885f1d5fda1dc559810349d776_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2558\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-081286f63ae55cb53353676beea9bd15_r.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e可半自定义的邮箱内容界面\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"VOJ_oXwZ\"\u003e之前用过网易邮箱大师（用了超过两年，有广告，而且每次换设备大部分账号，比如QQ，Gmail，学校账号需要重新设置，即使都挂在统一的网易账号下）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"edx8olOZ\"\u003eoutlook（用过两年，有狗皮膏药一样的bug，几年了没修复，除此之外很好，也是需要每次换设备设置）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"31uyTWZw\"\u003e苹果自带的（功能简单，每次更换设备需要设置）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"aLR6TS7D\"\u003e雷鸟（忘记了，似乎是外观不好看删掉了）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"is_thanked":false,"is_nothelp":false,"voting":0},"is_labeled":false,"visited_count":7138,"thumbnails":["https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9ef51779694037d556a63e7b5dd08907_720w.jpg?source=b6762063","https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-271b69830e357c0054dba7fc0846c24c_720w.jpg?source=b6762063"],"favorite_count":56,"answer_type":"normal","is_navigator":false,"navigator_vote":false,"vote_next_step":"vote"},"brief":"{\"source\": \"TS\", \"ty